data.name: ErrorNotMatchedFileNameAndClassName
data.value: The View class must have the same file name and class name.

data.name: ErrorMultipleHaikaraUiAttributeClass
data.value: Only one class with the HaikaraUI attribute can be defined in a single file.

data.name: ErrorNestedHaikaraUiAttributeClass
data.value: Nesting of classes with the HaikaraUI attribute is prohibited.

data.name: WarningMissingRelatedUxmlFile
data.value: The associated .uxml file was not found.

data.name: ErrorClickCommandHasNoEventBaseArgument
data.value: Methods with the ClickCommand attribute must have only EventBase as an argument.

data.name: WarningHaikaraUiHasNotImplementedValidInterface
data.value: Classes with the HaikaraUI attribute must implement IHaikaraView or IHaikaraStyle.
